Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在逐漸改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對教給我各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我相遇的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要由衷地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的…超級害羞 我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 對於諸位順利完成了所有課程的畢業生們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能以從這所歷史悠久的學校畢業為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你們能時時準備著向未來展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 愛麗絲前輩走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快去說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我…我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…愛麗絲前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳順利畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把妳制服的第二顆紐扣給我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也一直是妳的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真狡猾 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像沒告訴妳們今天是畢業典禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了畢業於相同學校的前輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳順利畢業 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝二位前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天 愛麗絲終於從中學畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平常一樣走路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得應該那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這是中學時期最後的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒走可是失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是超級No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有雅典娜前輩在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間就是靜止的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.89,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那陣 橙色和風之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟 要通過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小後輩 非常有幹勁呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 非常地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為以前在學校耽誤了的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後都能用來跟前輩們一起練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…超級高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們也向著正式領航員 Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是發聲練習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟 要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那愛麗絲從學校畢業後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在非常有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在感覺自己超級能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自己也感覺很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是覺得現在無論做什麼都能非常順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天去野餐好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 一定要去成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當的準備都完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級完美呢 雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天我來扮演客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲來扮演領航員帶我遊覽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受這個建議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雅典娜前輩現在開始就是我重要的客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲的笑容變得很自然了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我們好像是初次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我每天都在跟能夠給我最棒的笑容的前輩們練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一座是僅憑一個橋拱就橫跨了48米大運河的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里亞托橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這周圍與聖馬可廣場不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店 市場 酒店和居民區混雜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡可以感受到新威尼斯真實的民間生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可說是第二個城鎮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐的觀光解說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常清晰易懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我每天都被滿口禁止的前輩重點培訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來您想參觀什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您有想要參觀的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面是一片田園地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與這座著名的港口城市有著迥異的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您享受新威尼斯的另一種風情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ciao
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Buon giorno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您想再來杯茶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 不過不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是個野餐的好日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 現在剛好在下行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微等一會就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看上去這麼不可靠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非常可靠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦妳了 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個水上電梯到達頂部之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作模式切換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做什麼都沒問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確認為在跟前輩們開始練習後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的技術和觀光解說是變得有模有樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船歌就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來聲音很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不太擅長唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道自己有沒有放開聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道自己有沒有走調…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是覺得自己必須學好船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋裡就越是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己覺得唱得很辛苦的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽眾自然也會聽得很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌的技巧當然不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡唱歌這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連愛麗絲自己都不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有誰會去喜歡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地就在眼前了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎？領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說在這顆星球的地表上充滿海水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為AQUA之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個世界都是橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界被染上橙色的短短這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些住在水星的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會覺得非常眷戀 非常感懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡蘊藏著…我們的永遠一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是燈里前輩和藍華前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有剛才管理水上電梯的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的是公司的高層人員和鳳尾舟協會的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天真是太感謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最後能請妳唱首歌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您知道名揚水星的水之三大精靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣 我也是其中那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為風之精靈的領航員的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(398,440)\fs20}Seiren
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意弟子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我過去不擅長唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我小時候最喜歡的就是唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人的話讓我回想起了那時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司一直在等著妳從中學畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划船的技術非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都讓人擔心的觀光解說和客人的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後連船歌都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今天的考試裡展現出了顯著的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於擔負了水上領航協會下一代重任的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟協會給予了非常高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且懷著強烈的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出了前所未有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果斷的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 橙星公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始 妳就是正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙星…公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小後輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐫刻在水星歷史上的領航員的光輝歷程中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又誕生了前所未有的跳級成為正式領航員的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲小姐真的好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點崇拜她了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳 愛麗絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲成為正式領航員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就有這種預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超級超級緊張…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.58,0:24:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就要讓心情放鬆～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份 賞月之夜的心動…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
